' stuttered Casipeti.
`Thou hast a villainous name, cousin Iziziziz. Where wert thou born?
`Born?'
`Who had the begetting o' thee, that he gave thee such a heathenish han
dle for honest men's tongues to take hold o' thee by?'
`In Mexico.'
`And yonder Peruvian maiden, who hath not half thy years, was the
